Reasoning: The paper discusses SLAM approaches for navigation and tracking, which are common topics in robotics (cs.RO). The use of RGB-D sensors and Kinect Fusion algorithm suggests computer vision (cs.CV) as another likely sub-category. Machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) may also be relevant due to the use of algorithms for tracking and mapping. Finally, graphics (cs.GR) may be relevant due to the potential applications in augmented reality.
